### Health
GET {{baseUrlIAManager}}/health

### Retrieve de resource list (tables) from MCP
POST {{baseUrlMCP}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json, text/event-stream

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "method": "resources/list",
  "params": {},
  "id": 1
}

### Retrieve data from gig_db via assistant
###
POST {{baseUrlIAManager}}/assistants
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "prompt": "What are the available tables in the database?"
}

###
POST {{baseUrlIAManager}}/assistants
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "prompt": "What are the relations available within the tables?"
}

###
POST {{baseUrlIAManager}}/assistants
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "prompt": "What are the relations available from skills?"
}

### Simulate a user asking for a non existing table
